# A contributor's global ignore file can carry patterns that happen to match a
# directory this repository owns, silently excluding source. Re-including every
# tree makes the repository's own layout authoritative regardless of what a
# personal ignore file says. Kept in step with the tree by the source-tracked
# gate, which derives its list from the directories that exist.

